## Contributors

Future contributors may be recorded here or through Git history.

Contributions are accepted only under the repository's contribution terms and must
not introduce runtime execution, scanning, credential injection, customer-target
operation, or sensitive vulnerability disclosure without explicit review and
maintainer acceptance.
